    "Hey, I'm Thore! A podcaster and software developer from the Ruhr area. I've loved Dong Open Air for many years, and this app is basically my little love letter to the festival." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Moin, ich bin Thore! Podcaster und Softwareentwickler aus dem Ruhrgebiet. Das Dong Open Air liebe ich schon seit vielen Jahren, und diese App ist quasi mein kleiner Liebesbrief an das Festival."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Hey, I'm Thore! A podcaster and software developer from the Ruhr area. I've loved Dong Open Air for many years, and this app is basically my little love letter to the festival."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I'm also a huge Magic: The Gathering fan. If we bump into each other at Dong, let's play a round. And if you enjoy the app, I'd be happy if you grabbed me a beer." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Außerdem bin ich ein riesiger Magic: The Gathering Fan. Wenn wir uns auf dem Dong über den Weg laufen, lass uns gerne eine Runde spielen. Und wenn dir die App gefällt, freue ich mich riesig über ein Bier."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "I'm also a huge Magic: The Gathering fan. If we bump into each other at Dong, let's play a round. And if you enjoy the app, I'd be happy if you grabbed me a beer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
